comments: Jones (NOP) is firming up on his left foot as he establishes himself in Fontecchio's (UTA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Yurtseven (UTA) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.

Daniels (NOP) delivers contact to George (UTA) and dislodges him from his position.
